ha.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/z5862894949389_ac2fa142164ceffd23c448237440f409-300x300.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" srcset=\"https://www.cavaha.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/z5862894949389_ac2fa142164ceffd23c448237440f409-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.cavaha.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/z5862894949389_ac2fa142164ceffd23c448237440f409-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.cavaha.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/z5862894949389_ac2fa142164ceffd23c448237440f409-100x100.jpg 100w, https://www.cavaha.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/z5862894949389_ac2fa142164ceffd23c448237440f409.jpg 500w\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-21413\" src=\"https://www.cavaha.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/z5862894949390_b3f31a620f5ef4345564938f56f36c13-e1727171864820-300x254.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" srcset=\"https://www.cavaha.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/z5862894949390_b3f31a620f5ef4345564938f56f36c13-e1727171864820-300x254.jpg 300w, https://www.cavaha.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/z5862894949390_b3f31a620f5ef4345564938f56f36c13-e1727171864820.jpg 500w\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"508\"></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Có đủ kích thước cho các dòng xe phổ biến ở Việt Nam</li>\r\n<li>Ôm vừa sát khít hoàn toàn vào vô lăng – lắp đặt cực kỳ đơn giản</li>\r\n<li>Cực kỳ phù hợp cho người thường xuyên bị ra mồ hôi tay, lái xe đường dài.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-21414\" src=\"https://www.cavaha.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/z5862894949392_4aa5433b380172aed067b9df026e7ad0-300x300.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" srcset=\"https://www.cavaha.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/z5862894949392_4aa5433b380172aed067b9df026e7ad0-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.cavaha.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/z5862894949392_4aa5433b380172aed067b9df026e7ad0-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.cavaha.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/z5862894949392_4aa5433b380172aed067b9df026e7ad0-100x100.jpg 100w, https://www.cavaha.com/wp